snippet.title: LOFI Katana | Official Trailer 2 | Release in July 2023
snippet.description:
Hey everyone,

We are very proud to present you the second official trailer of LOFI Katana announcing its release date which is coming very soon !

We would be very thankful if you could add it to your wishlist on Steam:https://store.steampowered.com/app/1723680/LOFI_Katana/

Feel free to join our discord, we would be happy to discuss with you !
https://discord.gg/f4Jpnzpwen

Take care :)

Music: Mizuki - Bad Snacks

Follow us on our other socials
https://www.instagram.com/lofi.katana
https://twitter.com/LofiKatana
https://www.tiktok.com/@lofi.katana
